snippet.title: Funny babies & kids make us smile and laugh! - Funny and cute compilation
snippet.description:
Super funny, humorous and cute compilation about babies, toddlers and kids! I'm sure this compilation will make you laugh and smile! Here are the funniest kids driving toy cars, failing at sports, sleeping, dancing, eating,... What is your favourite clip? :) Hope you like our compilation, please share it and SUBSCRIBE! Watch also our other videos!

WANT TO SEE YOUR PET IN OUR COMPILATIONS?
Send your clips or links to: tigerlicensing@gmail.com

For more funny videos & pictures visit and like our Facebook page:
https://www.facebook.com/tigerstudiosfun
